Titolo: Alone in the Dark 3

Anno: 1994

Descrizione: Alone in the Dark 3 is the third installment of the Alone in the Dark survival horror video game series developed and published by Infogrames Multimedia. The video game was released for MS-DOS in 1994. It was ported to the PC-98 in 1995. Versions for Windows and Mac OS were also released in 1996 under the name of Alone in the Dark: Ghosts in Town.